* SKY130 flat model -- NMOS Id-Vd family curves
* Runs in LTspice (open as netlist, Run) and ngspice (ngspice idvd_nmos.cir)
.include ../sky130_ptm_style.lib
.option scale=1u

M1 d g 0 0 sky130_nmos_130 L=0.15 W=1
Vd d 0 1.8
Vg g 0 0

* Vd swept 0->1.8V, for Vg = 0.6,0.9,1.2,1.5,1.8V
.dc Vd 0 1.8 0.02 Vg 0.6 1.8 0.3

* --- LTspice: after Run, add trace Id(M1) ---
* --- ngspice batch: uncomment the control block below ---
*.control
*run
*plot -i(Vd)
*.endc
.end
